content: Reviewed our trading journal again with my mentor. We're seeing clear progress in managing emotional responses. It's like I've been given a new set of eyes.
Got an email from the firm. They're impressed with our quantum algorithm integration progress. They've greenlit the next phase. We're on track!
AI patent application is submitted. Now, we wait. But this feels like the end of a chapter and the beginning of something bigger. Here's to hoping.
